      "intent": "analysis",
      "content": "| Line item | FY22 | FY23 | TTM Jun-24 |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Revenue | 512 | 588 | 624 |\n| Gross profit | 392 | 459 | 491 |\n| EBITDA | 118 | 147 | 161 |\n| EBITDA margin | 23.0% | 25.0% | 25.8% |\n- Revenue growth is mainly transaction volume-led with selective pricing uplift in enterprise channels.\n- Gross margin expansion reflects better pass-through recovery and processing efficiency.\n- EBITDA conversion improved despite reinvestment in support capacity.",
