      "title": "Margin Bridge",
      "intent": "multi-driver-analysis",
      "content": "- Baseline margin FY22: 23.0\n- Mix shift contribution: 1.2\n- Pricing contribution: 0.9\n- Productivity contribution: 1.1\n- Inflation and support drag: -0.4\n- Net margin TTM Jun-24: 25.8\n- Bridge indicates expansion is quality-led rather than one-off accounting effects.",
