    {
      "id": "qofe-style-adjustments",
      "title": "QofE-Style Adjustments",
      "intent": "recommendations",
      "content": "- Adj #1: remove non-recurring settlement credit (+2.1 EBITDA impact).\n- Adj #2: normalize staffing to run-rate after temporary vacancy lag (-1.3 EBITDA impact).\n- Adj #3: align support software costs to contracted run-rate (-0.7 EBITDA impact).\n- Reported EBITDA margin: 25.8%; normalized EBITDA margin: 25.1%.\n- Interpretation: earnings quality remains strong; normalization reduces upside narrative but improves comparability.",
